Description: Paper and paperboard; articles of paper pulp, of paper or of paperboard

Subentries.Description: Cartons, boxes, cases, bags and other packing containers, of paper, paperboard, cellulose wadding or webs of cellulose fibers; box files, letter trays and similar articles, of paper or paperboard of a kind used in offices, shops or the like:
Sacks and bags, having a base of a width of 40 cm or more
Shipping sacks and multiwall bags, other than grocers' bags
